{
  "stem": "12491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody in the camp was assigned a date at which he has to work there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I believe I was there three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Eventually, since the camp was to be evacuated, rumors started going on that people are going to go to Gusen, people are going to go to Mauthausen, people are going to go to many other camps-- I don't remember them all by name-- and that some people will be going with Schindler to Czechoslovakia to his munition factory.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But these people are being-- the list for these people is being prepared at that time, and Schindler will decide who are the people that he will take with him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "While the list was being prepared, I was looking for ways to get on that list-- for my sister, my brother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I did put all three of us on the list through contacts of my friends, even though it was very difficult because I was not at Schindler's-- none of us were at Schindler's originally, and these people had the priority.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were 300 of them, but he wanted 1,100.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people were-- what people do not realize, people still had some valuables with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The valuables were diamonds, which they put into their molar teeth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they realized that the ghetto was going to be liquidated, many people had their molar teeth drilled out, put diamonds in them, and filled.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was the means by which people got on the list.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They removed the diamonds from their teeth, and they paid up to get on the list.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, these people are in Plaszow right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard about him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that Schindler has a site camp like the airport camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
